    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J22">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>All these my banners be.</l>
                    <l>I sow my pageantry In May --</l>
                    <l>It rises train by train --</l>
                    <l>Then sleeps in state again --</l>
                    <l>My chancel -- all the plain</l>
                    <l>Today.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To lose -- if one can find again --</l>
                    <l>To miss -- if one shall meet --</l>
                    <l>The Burglar cannot rob -- then --</l>
                    <l>The Broker cannot cheat.</l>
                    <l>So build the hillocks gaily</l>
                    <l>Thou little spade of mine</l>
                    <l>Leaving nooks for Daisy</l>
                    <l>And for Columbine --</l>
                    <l>You and I the secret</l>
                    <l>Of the Crocus know --</l>
                    <l>Let us chant it softly --</l>
                    <l>"There is no more snow!"</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To him who keeps an Orchis' heart --</l>
                    <l>The swamps are pink with June.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
